claim.claim-text:
1. An apparatus for attaching a boat cover to a boat, comprising:
an elongated member defining a first leg and a second leg;
a plurality of notches defined in the first leg of the elongated member;
a flexible cover affixed to the second leg of the elongated member along at least one edge;
a guide affixable to a deck of a boat, the guide defining at least one securement groove therein, the securement groove accepting the second leg of the elongated member therein,
wherein the elongated member is affixed to the flexible cover via stitching between the second leg and the flexible cover.
